{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 292433, "create_time": 1657720850, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "即便中国能“民主化”了，不管通过一人一票还是代议制的方式，如此大基数渴望搞阶级跃迁——“王侯将相宁有种乎”的群体，选择的社会模式也不会是高福利的。", "timestamp": 1657720850}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 292470, "create_time": 1657721874, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 那就消灭阶级", "timestamp": 1657721874}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 292483, "create_time": 1657722224, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 什么一步登天", "timestamp": 1657722224}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 292517, "create_time": 1657723671, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Bob接受啊", "timestamp": 1657723671}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 292620, "create_time": 1657726240, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "福利国家？是个好的制度吗？", "timestamp": 1657726240}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 292621, "create_time": 1657726262, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "或者说，是个进步的制度嘛", "timestamp": 1657726262}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293083, "create_time": 1657735243, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 问题的关键也是我想表达的，中国人并不会认为福利国家是进步的制度，因为这妨碍了人们当人上人的追求。而这种观念是由充满竞争的教育模式甚至社会环境塑造的。", "timestamp": 1657735243}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293091, "create_time": 1657735515, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 福利制度的反对者未必是一个意见，我并不介意福利，但是福利占据大多数社会资源，是我不认同的，毕竟我还做着星辰大海那虚无缥缈的梦", "timestamp": 1657735515}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293101, "create_time": 1657735802, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 理解你的想法。我隐含的是：目前树洞键政圈的风向是对福利社会的向往，但似乎在现实中并没有多少人认可", "timestamp": 1657735802}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293104, "create_time": 1657735947, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "我不懂，福利制度是指学历高低都能拿到一样的酬劳吗", "timestamp": 1657735947}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293108, "create_time": 1657736061, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Dave: 这样的话就不用卷哩诶嘿嘿（x）", "timestamp": 1657736061}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293109, "create_time": 1657736074, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 不是。", "timestamp": 1657736074}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293112, "create_time": 1657736178, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 个人当然是更倾向福利社会啊，这无可厚非，但是在政治的角度上，就不应该只顾着眼前的收益了。\n我不觉得民主制是什么好东西，民主应该被政治服务，而非服务于政治，就这一点我已经和树洞建政圈很不相容了，但那又有什么关系，终归只是建政而已。睡觉啦睡觉啦，晚安晚安", "timestamp": 1657736178}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293113, "create_time": 1657736205, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 一样酬劳×罗尔斯的差异原则（勉强可以这么理解）", "timestamp": 1657736205}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293177, "create_time": 1657757480, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "有言论自由之后观念是可以变的啊", "timestamp": 1657757480}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 293468, "create_time": 1657771351, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Carol: 你这远视主义者，你难道不知道只有宽松的社会环境才能持续地诞生能实行星辰大海的科学技术吗", "timestamp": 1657771351}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 294952, "create_time": 1657844794, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 但是不应该让福利占据大多数资源啊，福利只需要足以维护宽松的社会环境就够了，多数资源还是应该投入生产和科研", "timestamp": 1657844794}], "create_time": 1657720659, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657844794, "likenum": 9, "n_attentions": 9, "n_comments": 17, "pid": 82678, "poll": null, "reply": 17, "text": "假如中国成为了发达国家（不管通过产业升级还是什么手段，假设可以），我们就一定能建立“福利国家”吗？\n不谈中国长久以来的间接税传统（与福利国家的直接税体系不同），单从民众观念上来看。浸淫在12年的高考长跑制度中的新一代年轻人，接受的观念都是“吃得苦中苦方为人上人”、“万般皆下品惟有读书高”，按照这种单一价值观，意味着高直接税的现代福利社会体系就是“养懒汉”、“不尊重知识分子”的体现——毕竟读了这么多年书，怎么能让通过“非读书途径”的、“没有取得高学历”的那群人和“知识分子群体”拿差不多的工资？\n福利国家似乎并不是中国所认可的现代发展模式。", "timestamp": 1657720659}}